=Review=

"It is a profoundly simple and low quality video but the online video available here of [[Eben Moglen]] presenting and elaborating on ‘The DotCommunist Manifesto’ conveyed the kind of excitement to me that I like to imagine John Reed must have felt listening to those ranting in cellars in the days preceding the Russian Revolution."
